reviewText: yet another fantastic civil war collection. Definite must for the civil war buff!
A great way to learn a lot about a small but significant part of American History.
Fantastic collection, fast service, good resource, received as advertised.
It's not allot of dough, so worth a look and a great addition to any home collection of Civil War / historical films and documentaries.  A great collection at a great price.
